---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "Clay Bar Treatment Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Professional clay bar treatment in Fort Lauderdale. Removes embedded contaminants for glass-smooth paint. Mobile service. Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: `${base}car-wash-fort-lauderdale/`,
  title: "Car Wash Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Clay Bar Treatment Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="Clay bar treatment removes embedded contaminants from your paint that washing alone can't touch, leaving a glass-smooth surface ready for wax or sealant."
  currentPage="/clay-bar-treatment-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Run your hand across your car's paint after washing. If it feels rough or gritty, that's contamination embedded in your clear coat. Industrial fallout, brake dust, tree sap, overspray, and rail dust all bond to paint and won't come off with soap alone.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Clay bar treatment uses a specially formulated clay compound that safely pulls these contaminants out of your paint. The result is a perfectly smooth surface that reflects light evenly and allows wax to bond properly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We bring clay bar treatment directly to your Fort Lauderdale location. This service is essential preparation before any waxing or paint protection application.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Much Does Clay Bar Treatment Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Clay bar treatment in Fort Lauderdale costs $75 to $150 depending on vehicle size and contamination level.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Heavily contaminated vehicles that haven't been clayed in years require more time and clay. We assess your paint's condition and provide an exact quote.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Long Does Clay Bar Treatment Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Clay bar treatment takes 1 to 2 hours depending on vehicle size and how contaminated the paint is.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We work one section at a time, using plenty of lubricant to ensure the clay glides safely without marring your paint. Rushing this process causes scratches, so we take the time to do it right.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Why Does Your Car Need Clay Bar Treatment?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Contaminants embed in your clear coat and can't be removed by washing. Clay bar safely extracts them without damaging your paint.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Common contaminants that require clay bar removal:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Industrial fallout from factories and construction</li>
          <li>Brake dust from your wheels and other vehicles</li>
          <li>Rail dust if you park near train tracks</li>
          <li>Overspray from nearby painting projects</li>
          <li>Tree sap residue that doesn't wash off</li>
          <li>Tar and road film</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Fort Lauderdale vehicles accumulate contaminants faster due to our proximity to the ocean (salt), airport (jet fuel deposits), and I-95 (road grime and brake dust).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Our Clay Bar Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Wash First</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We hand wash your vehicle to remove loose dirt. Clay works on bonded contaminants, not surface dirt.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Contamination Check</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We feel the paint to identify the most contaminated areas and determine how much work is needed.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Lubricate Surface</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We spray clay lubricant generously. The clay must glide—never drag—across your paint.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Clay Application</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We gently rub the clay bar across each panel. Contaminants transfer from your paint to the clay.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Wipe and Check</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We wipe away lubricant and feel the paint. If still rough, we repeat. If smooth, we move to the next section.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-2">Best When Paired With Wax</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Clay bar treatment is ideal preparation for waxing. Once contaminants are removed, wax bonds directly to clean paint and lasts longer. We recommend combining these services.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Clay Bar Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#c9a227] font-bold">$</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">$75-$150 depending on size</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">1-2 hours</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Removes contaminants</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Glass-smooth finish</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Prep for wax</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Book Clay Bar Treatment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
            Same-day appointments available throughout Fort Lauderdale.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            754-215-2272
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href={`${base}car-waxing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Car Waxing</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}hand-wash-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Hand Wash</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}water-spot-removal-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Water Spot Removal</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}full-detail-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Full Detail</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
